example 3. frost elites in GD send in pet, pet dies.<br>
yes it is possible to kill these mobs IF u nuke when u send in pet. however the 57 earth pet DIES against every dark blue con mob i have ever sent it against even when nuking as fast as i can.  fine a pet shouldnt be able to solo a dark blue... but ice giants are TWENTY $*#^ING LVLS lower than me and it kills my pet. thats balance /boggle. what kind of crack are u smoking.<br>
example WIZ, soloing wyrverns in CS, can quad kite FOUR at a time 3 times in a row for 12 TOTAL on one mana burn, druid same thing, a Mage can do maybe 3 then she is OOM and gets to spend TWELVE minutes medding at lvl 58 to full mana. again you call this balance???? mind u wyverns are lvl 40 mobs and LIGHT blue at 58 but GEE they stomp such a mud hole in pet i must summon a new pet for each wyvern i attack and that costs mana.<br>
this is NOT a flame but explain to me how mobs 20 lvls lower than me kill my 57earth pet and that im balanced /boggle<br>
