also i know silverwind is gonna argue he can chain summon pets etc etc however u burn a LOT of mana making sure u do MORE than 50 percent dmg of pet so u dont get $*$#^@ on exp.<br>
Mages are supposed to be a SOLO class PERIOD. we arent and posting all the wananbe dps $*@) in the world wont change the FACTS that mages suck. <br>
OH side note mage EPIC /ROFL, any 60 lvl wiz/druid/shm/ necro/ranger can solo the dino in OOT. it takes THREE epic pets to get the job done. yea some balance. verrant said they made mages epic the hardest to do becuae it is the best. well only FOUR pets can engage a mob at any time so they made sure there was NO balance issue in mages useing epics to kill high lvl mobs. and then they claim how special our epic is and yet grp classes can SOLO mobs our epic pet cant, remmeber it takes THREE Epic pets to do what ONE ranger etc etc can do in oot killing the dino. <br>
